[[TouchArcade|TouchArcade]]给出了5分的满分，称《狂野飙车8》是狂野飙车系列的“顶峰之作”。编辑被游戏中新的图像性能和空中飞跃动作所吸引。他说道“iOS平台已经成为伟大赛车游戏的天堂，而《狂野飙车8》看起来是其中最伟大的游戏”。<ref name="Arcade">{{cite web|url=http://toucharcade.com/2013/08/21/asphalt-8-review/|title='Asphalt 8: Airborne' Review - An Amazing Arcade Racing Experience|publisher=TouchArcade|first=Eric|last=Ford|date=August 21, 2013|accessdate=September 6, 2013|archive-date=2013-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130914200629/http://toucharcade.com/2013/08/21/asphalt-8-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[AppSpy|AppSpy]]的编辑James Gilmour同样给出了5分的满分。他赞扬游戏的操控性，卡车的安排，赛车和更新。<ref name="Spy">{{cite web|url=http://www.appspy.com/review/7671/asphalt-8-airborne|title=Asphalt 8: Airborne Review|publisher=AppSpy|first=James|last=Gilmour|date=September 3, 2013|accessdate=September 6, 2013|archive-date=2013-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130906121124/http://www.appspy.com/review/7671/asphalt-8-airborne|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[MacLife|MacLife]]编辑Andrew Hayward 给出了5分满分。他认为这部作品将会是成为这类赛车游戏中最好的一部。<ref name="Mac">{{cite web|url=http://www.maclife.com/article/reviews/asphalt_8_airborne_review|title=Asphalt 8: Airborne Review|publisher=''[[MacLife|MacLife]]''|first=Andrew|last=Hayward|date=August 22, 2013|accessdate=September 6, 2013|archive-date=2013-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130908111830/http://www.maclife.com/article/reviews/asphalt_8_airborne_review|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[148Apps|148Apps]]打出了4.5分（满分5分）并评论道游戏带领狂野飙车系列走向了一个新的高度。<ref name="148Apps">{{cite web|url=http://www.148apps.com/reviews/asphalt-8-airborne-review/|title=Asphalt 8: Airborne Review|publisher=148Apps|first=Andrew|last=Stevens|date=August 22, 2013|accessdate=September 6, 2013|archive-date=2013-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130827123149/http://www.148apps.com/reviews/asphalt-8-airborne-review/|dead-url=no}}</ref> [[Gamezebo|Gamezebo]]的编辑同样打出了4.5分（满分5分）。<ref name="Gamezebo">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamezebo.com/games/asphalt-8-airborne/review|title=Asphalt 8: Airborne Review|publisher=[[Gamezebo|Gamezebo]]|first=David|last=Oxford|date=August 27, 2013|accessdate=September 6, 2013|archive-date=2013-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130903070106/http://www.gamezebo.com/games/asphalt-8-airborne/review|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[Pocket_Gamer|Pocket Gamer]] 在10分中打出了9分，还给出了“金奖”的评价。他称赞道：“街机式赛车套装游戏，真是出类拔萃。”<ref name="Pocket">{{cite web|url=http://www.pocketgamer.co.uk/r/iPad/Asphalt+8%3A+Airborne/review.asp?c=53273|title=Asphalt 8: Airborne Review|publisher=[[Pocket_Gamer|Pocket Gamer]]|first=Harry|last=Slater|date=August 22, 2013|accessdate=September 6, 2013|archive-date=2018-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180917074743/http://www.pocketgamer.co.uk/r/iPad/Asphalt+8%3A+Airborne/review.asp?c=53273|dead-url=no}}</ref>

